  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2873760/extras/131bc00224040da3ed2c1b81373c41a2.poster.avif?t=1719475820\" width=640 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2873760/extras/131bc00224040da3ed2c1b81373c41a2.webm?t=1719475820\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>“Beauties! They're All After Me” is an immersive video game of the love simulation type. What makes it different is that it incorporates the characteristics of the current cool drama into the game - the male protagonist awakens the cheating system. With the help of the cheating system, the kneeling and licking spare tires in reality do not exist, and all of them are brainless girls chasing boys! Various super sweet close-ups, and have a hearty love (or several) with the beauties!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2873760/extras/693c2b62bfca4a88e74d17e3a4df8b13.poster.avif?t=1719475820\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2873760/extras/693c2b62bfca4a88e74d17e3a4df8b13.webm?t=1719475820\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2873760/extras/693c2b62bfca4a88e74d17e3a4df8b13.mp4?t=1719475820\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Murong Qingxue, pure and kind, childhood sweetheart Bai Yueguang, has always had a crush on the male protagonist.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2873760/extras/6efbcf4cdce0554ca7655de973e90180.poster.avif?t=1719475820\" width=600 height=338 